content: Beautiful twists and turns, hopping back and forth between stories trying to get things straight only to realize you accidentally unlocked something else… started on the web version and was very glad to see that there was an option to start off from where the demo left off. Definitely need some time to mull over what all just happened…
Ok, I have no idea what this game is about, but I'm hooked. I can't explain what the hell is going on through 85%, but I beat it, I think?
Amazing form of storytelling and beautiful music
